name: Kissing penis [Concept]
description:
Kissing penis concept trained on 154 unique images. Not to be confused with fellatio, this is solely for the act of putting lips on a penis.

This lora was trained on two specific angles: pov and from side so it should be fairly flexible in its generation. Also include 1girl, 1boy for more consistent results.

NOTE: pov seems to have trained the better of the two. I may make a v2 at some point to better balance the training.

You can also mix in between breasts, handjob, ejaculation, and precum as modifiers. While these concepts weren't trained specifically, there were enough images in the dataset where they should be easy to prompt. As a heads up, pov tends to default to between breasts, especially with larger breast sizes. If you don't want that, just put it in the negative prompt.

You can use the sample prompts as a rough guide.
